billionaire chief executive officer of a US public company who has ever off=
ered to take a public company private=C2=A0<em>as a joke</em>. I wrote:</p>=
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Musk has some history here: In 201=
8 he pretended that he was going to take Tesla Inc. private; he wasn=E2=80=
