idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;">in Stratechery today</a>. =E2=80=9CIn my opinion,=E2=80=
=9D he writes,=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cthis analysis is extremely compelling evidence=
